#: ../../manual/scene_layout/object/editing/transform/introduction.rst:4
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "简介"

#: ../../manual/scene_layout/object/editing/transform/introduction.rst:6
msgid ""
"Transformations refer to a number of operations that can be performed on "
"a selected Object or Mesh that alters its position or characteristics."
msgstr "变换是指可以在所选物体或网格上对其位置或特征进行更改的操作。"

#: ../../manual/scene_layout/object/editing/transform/introduction.rst:9
msgid ""
"Each object can be moved, rotated and scaled in *Object Mode*. However, "
"not all of these transformations have an effect on all objects. For "
"example, scaling a camera has no effect on the render dimensions."
msgstr ""
"每个物体都可以在 *物体模式* 中移动、旋转和缩放。但是，并不是所有这些变换"
"都会影响所有的物体。例如，缩放相机对渲染尺寸没有影响。"

#: ../../manual/scene_layout/object/editing/transform/introduction.rst:13
msgid ""
":doc:`Basic transformations </scene_layout/object/editing/transform/"
"basics>` include:"
msgstr ""
":doc:`基础变换 </scene_layout/object/editing/transform/basics>` 包括："

#: ../../manual/scene_layout/object/editing/transform/introduction.rst:16
msgid "Moving"
msgstr "移动"

#: ../../manual/scene_layout/object/editing/transform/introduction.rst:17
msgid "Rotating"
msgstr "旋转"

#: ../../manual/scene_layout/object/editing/transform/introduction.rst:18
msgid "Scaling"
msgstr "缩放"

#: ../../manual/scene_layout/object/editing/transform/introduction.rst:20
msgid ""
"These three transforms are the three big ones. However, more advanced "
"transformations can be found in the :doc:`Advanced Transformations </"
"scene_layout/object/editing/transform/index>` section."
msgstr ""
"这是最基本的三种变换，可以在 :doc:`高级变换 </scene_layout/object/"
"editing/transform/index>` 章节找到更多高级变换。"

#: ../../manual/scene_layout/object/editing/transform/introduction.rst:23
msgid ""
"For making other changes to the geometry of editable objects, you should "
"use *Edit Mode*."
msgstr "要对可编辑物体的几何体进行其它更改，应使用 *编辑模式* 。"

#: ../../manual/scene_layout/object/editing/transform/introduction.rst:25
msgid ""
"Once you have added a basic object, you remain in *Object Mode*. You can "
"switch between *Object Mode* and *Edit Mode* by pressing :kbd:`Tab`. The "
"object's wireframe should now appear orange. This means that the object "
"is now selected and active."
msgstr ""
"一旦添加了一个基本物体，将仍然在 *物体模式* 中。可以通过按下 :kbd:`Tab` "
"在 *物体模式* 和 *编辑模式* 之间切换。该物体的线框现在应该显示为橙色。这"
"意味着物体现在被选中并激活。"
